      <title>使用rook搭建存储集群</title>
      <link>https://tangxusc.github.io/2019/03/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8rook%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4/</link>
